Police in Osun have arrested a man for allegedly filming a steamy session at the Osun Osogbo shrine. The Nation gathered that Jolaosho was arrested following a complaint by one Amoo Awosunwon. Awosunwon reported the case to the police in July after seeing a sex video on social media of Jolaosho allegedly dressed in Osun Osogbo attire with a naked lady at the Osogbo shrine. Police spokeswoman Yemisi Opalola confirmed the arrest on Sunday.